partnerDetails.about:
Our business focus originated in providing I.T and support services to the financial markets for stocks and foreign exchange trading platforms throughout Australia and New Zealand. We later identified that there was a growing demand in the horizontal and vertical markets to provide these services to both small and medium enterprises both locally and globally.

Our team of service desk operators, engineers, project managers and management staff have in excess of 30 years’ individual experience and contribute a broad, specialised wealth of knowledge in Information Technology. Our team are skilled, engaged, and motivated individuals with a strong focus on positive client outcomes.

Our service coverage compass the geographic territories of Australia, New Zealand and ASEAN and specialised EU/US markets. Our client base includes International & Australian Financial Institutions, Stock Exchanges, Telecommunication and Data Centre Providers, Global Software, SAAS and Cloud Services Companies, SDN and WDN fibre network appliance providers and Government, Non-for-Profit organisations and Small/Medium sized businesses.
